{"type":"user","uuid":"a8796889-0a3b-4703-b59b-1473644a65f4","session_id":"8cd881af-c16d-4c6e-b6da-7621419a768b","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019ce37654b757ab8f0d8581b920e824","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→DOC_LEVEL: L2\n   2→MODULE: runtime/services\n   3→PATH: src/services/**\n   4→DESCRIPTION: runtime service layer for chat/session/system actions plus pipeline control facade\n   5→\n   6→KEY_FILES:\n   7→- src/services/chat-service.js\n   8→- src/services/chat-queue.js\n   9→- src/services/session-store.js\n  10→- src/services/realtime-hub.js\n  11→- src/services/system-exec-service.js\n  12→- src/services/pipeline-control-service.js\n  13→- src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  14→- src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n  15→- src/services/status-aggregator.js\n  16→- src/services/log-pager.js\n  17→- src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  18→- src/services/git-service.js\n  19→- src/services/commit-service.js\n  20→- src/services/command-executor-service.js\n  21→- src/services/output-pager-service.js\n  22→\n  23→PUBLIC_APIS:\n  24→- chatWithSession({ channel, sessionId, message, realtimeHooks })\n  25→- resetSession({ channel, sessionId })\n  26→- pipeline control: startPipeline/getPipelineStatus/stopPipeline/retryTarget/getPipelineLogs/resetTarget\n  27→- pipeline controller (F-004): createPipelineController -> startPipeline/stopPipeline/retryTarget/runSingle/getStatus/getLogs/forceUnlock\n  28→- plan ingestion: validate/save/listVersions/getVersion/setCurrent/getCurrent/rollback/getActivePath\n  29→- status aggregator (F-005): createStatusAggregator -> aggregateStatus/formatStatusForTelegram/calculateProgress/getErrorSummary\n  30→- log pager (F-005): createLogPager -> readLogPage/extractErrorLines/shouldSendAsFile/formatLogsForTelegram\n  31→- telegram pusher (F-005): createTelegramPusher -> startHeartbeat/stopHeartbeat/pushErrorSummary/sendMessageChunked/sendFile\n  32→- git service (F-008): createGitService -> getStatus/isClean/getChangedFiles/commit/amendCommit/getLastCommit/getCommitLog/getShortHash\n  33→- commit service (F-008): createCommitService -> validatePreConditions/commit/recordCommit/getSessionCommits/checkPipelineStatus/checkTestStatus/buildCommitMessage\n  34→- command executor (F-009): executeCommand/confirmHighRiskCommand -> blacklist check, high-risk detection, confirmation flow, cwd support, output pagination\n  35→- output pager (F-009): paginateOutput/storeOutputPages/getNextPage/clearPages/hasMorePages -> Telegram 4096 char limit handling\n  36→\n  37→TRAPS:\n  38→- chat operations are serialized by session key; keep async queue semantics unchanged\n  39→- pipeline-control-service must delegate to script-runner instead of shell string concatenation\n  40→- pipeline-controller must use lock-manager for concurrency protection (F-004)\n  41→- runSingle must NOT acquire lock (independent execution, D5)\n  42→\n  43→DECISIONS:\n  44→- 2026-03-10 | f001-pipeline-service | expose logs/reset methods in pipeline-control-service to satisfy US3 reusable control surface\n  45→- 2026-03-12 | f003-plan-ingestion | add plan-ingestion-service for schema validation, version management, and plan registry\n  46→- 2026-03-12 | f004-pipeline-controller | new module for unified pipeline control with lock management (D4)\n  47→- 2026-03-13 | f005-status-logs | add status-aggregator, log-pager, telegram-pusher for pipeline status aggregation and log streaming\n  48→- 2026-03-15 | f008-commit-workflow | add git-service and commit-service for commit workflow with pre-commit validation, audit logging (AC-5.3)\n  49→- 2026-03-15 | f008-exception-handling | add try-catch blocks in commit() function around validatePreConditions, gitService.commit/amendCommit, recordCommit, logAuditEntry calls to prevent crashes and ensure errors logged to audit trail\n  50→- 2026-03-16 | f009-command-executor | add command-executor-service and output-pager-service for general shell command execution with blacklist, high-risk keywords, confirmation flow, session cwd, and pagination\n  51→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce371ea98df0b932fccfb717ee302","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T19:11:49.554Z","_requestId":"d4f8b50ec2ac4d7592e7518406c06130"}
