-999)\n 689→- Integration tests\n 690→- Documentation updates\n 691→- Prizm doc updates\n 692→\n 693→---\n 694→\n 695→## 8. Dependencies\n 696→\n 697→### 8.1 Existing Modules\n 698→\n 699→| Module | Usage |\n 700→|--------|-------|\n 701→| session-store | CWD tracking, state management |\n 702→| output-pager-service | Pagination for long output |\n 703→| param-sanitizer | Path validation, dangerous pattern detection |\n 704→| permission-guard | Role-based access control |\n 705→| audit-log-service | Operation logging |\n 706→| config | Allowed roots, limits configuration |\n 707→\n 708→### 8.2 New npm Dependencies\n 709→\n 710→None required. Use Node.js built-in `fs`, `path`, and `stream` modules.\n 711→For glob matching, consider adding `fast-glob` or implement minimatch manually.\n 712→\n 713→---\n 714→\n 715→## 9. Security Checklist\n 716→\n 717→- [ ] All paths validated against `TELEGRAM_FILE_ALLOWED_ROOTS`\n 718→- [ ] Path traversal (`..`) blocked\n 719→- [ ] Symbolic links resolved and re-validated\n 720→- [ ] File size limits enforced\n 721→- [ ] Binary file detection prevents accidental display\n 722→- [ ] Audit logging for all operations\n 723→- [ ] Role-based permissions enforced\n 724→- [ ] No shell command execution for file operations\n 725→\n 726→---\n 727→\n 728→## 10. Acceptance Criteria Mapping\n 729→\n 730→| AC | Implementation |\n 731→|----|----------------|\n 732→| AC-1.1 ~ AC-1.6 | listDirectory() + ls.js handler |\n 733→| AC-2.1 ~ AC-2.5 | buildTree() + tree.js handler |\n 734→| AC-3.1 ~ AC-3.7 | readFile() + cat/head/tail handlers |\n 735→| AC-4.1 ~ AC-4.6 | writeFile() + upload.js handler |\n 736→| AC-5.1 ~ AC-5.5 | download.js handler + existing file validation |\n 737→| AC-6.1 ~ AC-6.7 | searchFiles() + find.js handler |\n 738→| AC-7.1 ~ AC-7.5 | validatePath() + security integration |\n 739→\n 740→---\n 741→\n 742→## 11. Ready for Implementation\n 743→\n 744→**Plan Status**: ✅ Complete\n 745→**Next Step**: Generate tasks.md via prizmkit.ta