{"type":"user","uuid":"d26888cd-87cb-42e6-a38c-4634af0d6815","session_id":"8cd881af-c16d-4c6e-b6da-7621419a768b","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019ce37b9a2ef3f381d5548bbd1fd81d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1000→  // Tests for paginated output viewing\n1001→});\n1002→```\n1003→\n1004→### tests/services/output-pager-service.test.js (F-009 reference)\n1005→\n1006→```javascript\n1007→// Tests for paginateOutput, storeOutputPages, getNextPage, hasMorePages\n1008→```\n1009→\n1010→### tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js (F-006 reference)\n1011→\n1012→```javascript\n1013→// Tests for validatePath, detectDangerousPatterns, sanitizeParam\n1014→```\n1015→\n1016→---\n1017→\n1018→## Summary\n1019→\n1020→This context snapshot provides all the information needed for F-010 implementation:\n1021→\n1022→1. **Feature Requirements**: 7 acceptance criteria covering directory browsing, file viewing, file transfer, and search\n1023→2. **Existing Infrastructure**:\n1024→   - Session management with cwd support (session-store.js)\n1025→   - Output pagination system (output-pager-service.js)\n1026→   - Command routing and registration (bot/commands/)\n1027→   - Security layer with path validation (param-sanitizer.js, permission-guard.js)\n1028→   - File validation helpers in telegram.js\n1029→3. **Testing Patterns**: Node.js built-in test runner, async imports, mock contexts\n1030→\n1031→**Key Design Decisions for F-010**:\n1032→- Reuse `validatePath` from param-sanitizer for path security\n1033→- Integrate with existing `telegramFileAllowedRoots` config\n1034→- Follow existing command handler patterns from F-009 (/cd, /more)\n1035→- Use output-pager-service for long file content display\n1036→- Extend session-store if needed for file operation state\n1037→\n1038→---\n1039→\n1040→## Implementation Log\n1041→\n1042→### Files Created/Modified\n1043→\n1044→**New Files**:\n1045→- `src/services/file-service.js` - Core file operations service (validatePath, listDirectory, buildTree, readFile, searchFiles, writeFile, isBinaryFile, formatFileSize)\n1046→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/ls.js` - /ls and /dir command handler\n1047→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/tree.js` - /tree command handler\n1048→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/cat.js` - /cat command handler\n1049→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/head.js` - /head command handler\n1050→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/tail.js` - /tail command handler\n1051→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/find.js` - /find command handler\n1052→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/upload.js` - /upload command handler\n1053→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/download.js` - /download command handler\n1054→- `tests/services/file-service.test.js` - Unit tests for file service (30 tests)\n1055→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/ls.test.js` - Tests for /ls handler\n1056→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/tree.test.js` - Tests for /tree handler\n1057→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/cat.test.js` - Tests for /cat handler\n1058→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/head.test.js` - Tests for /head handler\n1059→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/tail.test.js` - Tests for /tail handler\n1060→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/find.test.js` - Tests for /find handler\n1061→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/upload.test.js` - Tests for /upload handler\n1062→- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/download.test.js` - Tests for /download handler\n1063→\n1064→**Modified Files**:\n1065→- `src/config.js` - Added FILE_MAX_READ_SIZE, FILE_MAX_TREE_DEPTH, FILE_MAX_TREE_ITEMS, FILE_MAX_SEARCH_DEPTH, FILE_MAX_SEARCH_RESULTS, FILE_SEARCH_RESULTS_PER_PAGE\n1066→- `src/services/session-store.js` - Added searchResultsBySessionKey methods for find pagination\n1067→- `src/bot/commands/registry.js` - Registered new file manager commands\n1068→\n1069→### Key Decisions\n1070→\n1071→1. **Path Validation**: Extended validatePath() to resolve symlinks and re-validate against allowed roots\n1072→2. **Binary Detection**: Check for null bytes in first 8KB of file\n1073→3. **Tree Building**: Recursive algorithm with configurable depth/item limits\n1074→4. **Glob Search**: Used minimatch package for pattern matching (fast-glob alternative)\n1075→5. **Upload Flow**: Supports reply-to-document pattern, auto-creates parent directories\n1076→6. **Download Flow**: Reuses validateFileForTelegram() from telegram.js, enforces 50MB limit\n1077→\n1078→### Deviations from Plan\n1079→\n1080→- Used minimatch instead of fast-glob for simpler dependency footprint\n1081→- Added symlink resolution in validatePath (addressed Reviewer's C-001 concern)\n1082→\n1083→### Test Results\n1084→\n1085→- File service tests: 30 passed\n1086→- Handler tests: All passing\n1087→- Pre-existing baseline failure: tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js:324 (sendFile)\n1088→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce378caca454e9924d63fde4cb32b","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T19:17:35.079Z","_requestId":"d4f8b50ec2ac4d7592e7518406c06130"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031303173517978a09d11843b0","session_id":"8cd881af-c16d-4c6e-b6da-7621419a768b","message":{"id":"2026031303173517978a09d11843b0","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019ce37ba450249675897e12f68912bd","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/010-file-manager/context-snapshot.md","old_string":"### Test Results\n\n- File service tests: 30 passed\n- Handler tests: All passing\n- Pre-existing baseline failure: tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js:324 (sendFile)","new_string":"### Test Results\n\n- File service tests: 30 passed\n- Handler tests: All passing\n- Pre-existing baseline failure: tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js:324 (sendFile)\n\n---\n\n## Review Notes\n\n### Review Date: 2026-03-13\n### Reviewer: Reviewer Agent (Phase 6)\n\n---\n\n### Issues Found\n\n| ID | Severity | File:Line | Description | Recommendation |\n|----|----------|-----------|-------------|----------------|\n| F-001 | MEDIUM | `file-utils.js:84` | AC-1.4 规格要求目录带 `/` 后缀，但实现使用 emoji 标记无后缀 | 建议：更新 spec.md 接受 emoji 方案为合理替代 |\n| F-002 | **HIGH** | `upload.js` | AC-4.4 未检查上传文件大小限制（Telegram 50MB） | 修复：在下载前检查 `document.file_size`，超过限制时拒绝 |\n| F-003 | **HIGH** | `upload.js` | AC-4.5 缺少覆盖确认流程，直接覆盖已存在文件 | 修复：添加确认机制，参考 F-009 的高风险命令确认流程 |\n| F-004 | MEDIUM | `ls.js, tree.js, cat.js, head.js, tail.js, find.js` | AC-7.4 缺少 audit logging（只有 upload/download 有） | 建议：为所有文件操作添加 `logAuditEntry` 调用 |\n| F-005 | LOW | `download.js:19` | `PHOTO_EXTENSIONS` 与 `file-utils.js:133` 的 `isImageExtension` 重复定义 | 建议：复用 `file-utils.js` 中的定义 |\n| F-006 | MEDIUM | `file-service.js:63-65` | 路径 `..` 检查在 `path.normalize()` 后执行，可能遗漏 edge case | 建议：在原始输入上检查 `..` 模式 |\n| F-007 | LOW | `file-service.js:440` | 变量 `truncated` 声明但未使用 | 修复：删除未使用变量 |\n| F-008 | LOW | `find.js:76-78` | 搜索结果存储到 session 但未提供分页获取后续页的机制 | 建议：扩展 `/more` 支持 find 结果或移除存储代码 |\n| F-009 | MEDIUM | `file-service.js:515-528` | `globToRegex` 转换逻辑可能不完整，字符类处理可能有边界问题 | 建议：添加更多复杂 glob 模式测试用例