anization | Good | 遵循现有架构模式 |\n| Error handling | Good | 中文错误消息，清晰的错误类型 |\n| Documentation | Adequate | JSDoc 注释完整 |\n| Test coverage | Good | 131 tests total (30 + 61 + 40) |\n| Consistency | Good | 与 F-009 模式一致 |\n\n---\n\n### Final Verdict\n\n## **PASS_WITH_WARNINGS**\n\n### Rationale\n\n1. **No CRITICAL issues** - 所有安全关键路径都有保护\n2. **Two HIGH issues** - F-002 (upload size check) 和 F-003 (overwrite confirmation) 需要修复\n3. **All tests passing** - 131 个测试全部通过\n4. **Spec compliance: 95%** - 38/40 AC 完全满足\n\n### Required Actions Before Release\n\n1. **F-002**: Add file size validation in `/upload` handler before downloading\n2. **F-003**: Add overwrite confirmation flow for existing files\n\n### Recommended Improvements (Non-blocking)\n\n1. F-004: Add audit logging to all file operations\n2. F-005: Deduplicate PHOTO_EXTENSIONS definition\n3. F-007: Remove unused `truncated` variable\n4. F-008: Implement `/more` for find results pagination\n\n---\n\n### COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n\n**Feature**: F-010 File Manager\n**Status**: PASS_WITH_WARNINGS\n**Next Action**: Fix F-002 and F-003 before production deployment\n**Blocker**: None - can proceed to next phase with noted warnings"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":87157,"output_tokens":1676,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce378caca454e9924d63fde4cb32b","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T19:18:05.042Z","_requestId":"d4f8b50ec2ac4d7592e7518406c06130"}
